Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:11.52,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, I believe you're aware of this, but time is short.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:14.69,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The Technician and Weapon written test.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:16.37,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,There is only three days until...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.65,0:03:17.87,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Super Written Exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:20.75,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you progressing with your studies?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:22.14,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:24.70,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been preparing since a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:28.09,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,All the questions this time were made by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.29,0:03:29.49,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Anxious ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:30.79,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Excited ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:33.57,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,There are lots of you who may feel that way, but give it your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:35.73,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, class dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:42.96,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no easy way to get it done, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.02,0:03:45.02,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's easy there's no point to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.11,0:03:47.01,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you if you use dirty methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:49.57,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be first this year too, Ox-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:50.77,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:55.37,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, last year I lost to Ox-kun, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:56.58,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:04:00.27,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are still some hard workers in the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:04.93,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, there's the second place Maka-san who lost to me last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.02,0:04:10.69,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why this test is so super?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:15.35,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a rumor of a jinx that whoever gets first place in this test is made into a Death Scythe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:16.46,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What? For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.35,0:04:18.16,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. {\alpha&HFF&}This is destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.16,0:04:19.44,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. This is destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:22.38,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama was in the top of the school too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:24.28,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get in the top as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.42,0:04:28.57,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I'll get first and turn Tsubaki into a Death Scythe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:29.54,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:32.67,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our first test.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:34.30,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:37.69,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't study to prepare myself for tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:39.17,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty full of yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:40.49,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:42.42,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:44.25,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand everything about souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.71,0:04:45.71,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.07,0:04:48.00,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This time there's Kid-kun too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:50.02,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of rivals, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:03.32,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:07.29,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Stein? I'm sending my daughter my "Do your best in the test" aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.39,0:05:08.50,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.00,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:12.02,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, carry on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:12.96,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:14.83,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Maka...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:19.43,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Maka!!
