Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:26.01,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Super Written Exam:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:28.99,Copy of Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fs44\pos(635,665)}~Heart-Throbbing, Trembling, Nervous, Lies?~ 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:28.55,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Heart-Throbbing, Trembling, Nervous, Lies? 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.94,0:05:34.96,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! One last spurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:37.69,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Maka, {\alpha&HFF&}are tests fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:39.69,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Maka, are tests fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:40.39,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:42.99,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You put to test all you've learned so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:45.50,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You can understand your ability easily through the points you get.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:47.22,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of like a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:51.55,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,But this time I have to put in an extra effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:54.98,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a jynx that if you get first place,\Nyou get to become a Death Scythe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.73,0:05:59.03,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Turning into a Death Scythe is hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:01.09,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome right? Maka's Papa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:02.67,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The awesome one is Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:05.71,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Turning a useless papa into a Death Scythe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:17.38,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Soul Knowledge subject...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:18.95,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What... {\alpha&HFF&}Soul-kun's studying too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:20.95,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What... Soul-kun's studying too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:22.61,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.87,0:06:23.51,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:27.07,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:28.66,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Blair is so bored!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:29.69,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:37.40,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Noisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:40.89,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,498...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:45.03,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,499...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:47.45,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,500...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:52.43,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't solve the next problem, I'll do 1000 crunches.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:54.03,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:55.58,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.33,0:07:10.38,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.79,0:07:12.87,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop with the penalties and study!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:14.49,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tutor you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:22.32,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The capable woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:23.82,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:25.20,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:26.48,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Study time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:27.66,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:29.67,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:29.67,Copy of Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:39.64,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're both studying so diligently...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:42.25,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need somethi- eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:43.89,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:45.30,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:48.04,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one strand that's sticking out...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:50.32,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It suddenly started bothering me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:53.14,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:55.32,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're plucking your eyebrows, let me do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:57.73,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do if they're not perfectly matched?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:08:01.65,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Last time I let you do this how long do you think it tooK?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:03.03,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,A whole month!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:03.94,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.99,0:08:05.02,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This time I'll do it fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:05.86,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:06.62,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:07.65,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... {\alpha&HFF&}Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:08.67,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.86,0:08:10.76,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If you must insist...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.86,0:08:11.99,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.49,0:08:13.68,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,First we'll start with the planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:15.12,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You're bothering my studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:15.72,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.34,0:08:17.88,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we choose for the concept?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.30,0:08:19.89,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Eyebrows with a story...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:21.64,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:24.98,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have such amazing eyebrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:09.97,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't eat anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:24.74,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's free to play...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.07,0:09:27.16,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Tests are pretty tough, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:39.76,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,With my body cleaned, it'll be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:44.22,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy that Black Star is really studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:46.63,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make him a snack later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:54.29,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops! I shouted!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.38,0:09:55.29,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Silently, {\alpha&HFF&}silently...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:56.34,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Silently, silently...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:10:00.36,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that quiet studying doesn't fit me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:04.26,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,As an assassin, I have to steal the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:08.94,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:12.83,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,With this I've become a god!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.43,0:10:15.22,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The god of the perfect score!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:30.83,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Star?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:33.37,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:46.48,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your studies?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:48.20,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:49.95,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Three days of break is more than enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:54.26,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It suddenly started bothering me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:10:59.50,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.50,0:11:04.50,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:11.10,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I've done what I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:13.78,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,To be fresh for tomorrow, I'll go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:20.16,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,May my daughter Maka... {\alpha&HFF&}Maka get first...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:21.21,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,May my daughter Maka... Maka get first...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:21.61,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,First... {\alpha&HFF&}first... first... tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:21.94,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,First... first... {\alpha&HFF&}first... tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:22.79,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,First... first... first... {\alpha&HFF&}tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.79,0:11:25.20,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,First... first... first... tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:27.03,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's test...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:29.52,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:35.59,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,So, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:38.10,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The Staff Super Written Exam results.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:40.12,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who thought "If I do it\N I can't do bad," they let their defense down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:43.98,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, the best scorer,\N the creator Ohkubo Atsushi, with 77 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:46.06,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasugawa Orino has done great too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.11,0:11:49.68,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The next one is the worst, Watanabe Misa-kun, with 6 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:51.27,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate you'll have to repeat the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:51.66,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Watanabe-kun, {\alpha&HFF&}you'll have to do supplementary classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:53.66,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Watanabe-kun, you'll have to do supplementary classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.33,0:12:01.58,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Sid, will be your examiner!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:03.86,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one thing before we begin the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:08.31,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.59,0:12:13.76,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, there was a fool that sneaked\N into Stein's lab to steal the test...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.45,0:12:17.77,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen well! Don't try to cheat on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:20.23,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The duration is 60 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:22.61,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your test sheets turned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:33.72,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:41.05,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:42.04,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:45.30,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who takes this seriously is an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:49.45,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,A tortoise with a late start has no chance against a hare.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:52.33,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is full of restless hares...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.02,0:12:54.55,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What method you use to win...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:57.25,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's all the same when you're doing the test!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:02.45,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I've hidden cheat sheets in my whole body!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:06.70,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't win easily there's no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:10.04,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to win... {\alpha&HFF&}win.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.04,0:13:10.93,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to win... win.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:14.29,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this all?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:17.09,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon! You want me to take off my underwear too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:18.57,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:20.24,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back to your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:21.56,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll forgive you once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.70,0:13:22.78,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the man I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:24.12,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.39,0:13:28.17,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:29.78,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Focus, focus...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:32.26,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The next question is filling in the blanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:36.72,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,"Complete the following sentence:"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:38.88,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,"A healthy soul..."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:41.17,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy... peace of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:42.70,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,"...resides in a healthy..."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:44.61,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,"...skin and..."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.70,0:13:47.64,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,"...in healthy cuticles."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:51.72,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's definitely wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.78,0:13:54.73,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't answered a single question yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:57.05,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This just ain't cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.72,0:13:59.71,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:02.76,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The perfectiontionist Kid is next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:15.66,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:17.29,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't write it nicely...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:19.57,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't even wrote his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:21.00,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.51,0:14:22.49,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,To the left we have...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:24.86,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Writing with crayon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.64,0:14:30.60,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,She's putting a lot of yellow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.78,0:14:34.82,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Giraffe! {\alpha&HFF&}Giraffe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.82,0:14:35.66,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Giraffe! Giraffe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:39.65,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,So you like that color.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:42.39,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer true or false...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:43.72,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.83,0:14:45.34,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly what to expect from Professor Stein.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.81,0:14:47.41,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a trick question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.19,0:14:49.18,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Trick question?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:51.40,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.94,0:14:54.37,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The Professor whouldn't fool the students.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:57.11,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,False!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.67,0:15:00.11,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fool me this easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:02.69,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, I'm already done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.35,0:15:05.11,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! You can read a book if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:13.83,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What a geek...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.12,0:15:23.18,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,10 minutes left!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:24.31,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:25.88,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time left!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:28.65,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid still hasn't wrote his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:29.95,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:30.48,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:33.53,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Giraffe! Giraffe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.69,0:15:35.48,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You made art out of the question sheets?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:38.88,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go break yo neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:40.93,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,In a way, she's a genius?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:42.04,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... {\alpha&HFF&}it's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:42.83,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... it's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:46.60,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... it's... no... use...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:50.63,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the "K" spaced wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.07,0:15:54.15,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a useless scumbag...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:58.19,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even place a "K" the right way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:13.37,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, Kid's unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:14.38,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave him be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:19.29,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:22.29,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:34.93,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You're writing with the blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:36.79,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, {\alpha&HFF&}you saw the answers in the lab, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.79,0:16:39.08,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, you saw the answers in the lab, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:41.03,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And you intend to pass them onto me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:42.66,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.01,0:16:44.87,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I will inherit your will!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:02.40,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about your sign!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:05.55,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk after you're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.84,0:17:06.99,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Only 30 seconds left!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.62,0:17:11.26,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:13.37,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I reviewed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:19.29,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,10 seconds left!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:21.04,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,With this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.99,0:17:27.00,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,5 seconds left!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:29.48,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:34.06,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:35.52,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:36.99,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.89,0:17:39.99,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:41.85,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.13,0:17:46.26,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It was over when I lost my pants...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:17:57.77,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Man that was hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.77,0:17:58.42,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiring, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.42,0:17:59.45,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It was hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:00.86,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It may have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:01.56,Copy of Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Really now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:02.51,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It seriously was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:41.95,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll beat yourself up, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:44.65,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done with the test and you're already studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:46.51,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:51.55,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,When I cleaned the room from studying, I found an old album.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:56.26,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you and your perverted Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:57.92,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,So young...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.14,0:18:58.88,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:01.82,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when papa was 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.00,0:19:05.56,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,He used to read me lots of picture books...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:11.17,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Your book addiction comes from your Dad, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:18.16,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it does...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:20.52,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:20.52,Copy of Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.83,0:19:22.74,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa-san, congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:25.09,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The test results came out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.15,0:19:27.06,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,With this I can drink something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.28,0:19:35.16,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Blair knows, you sent your aura for three days and nights, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:39.00,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Maka's amazing, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:41.69,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,She's at the top of her class, just as my wife was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:43.42,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Ex-wife, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.84,0:19:46.93,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:49.66,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Blair-chan, do you mind me asking you a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:53.34,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to give Maka something to congratulate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.43,0:19:56.99,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you could buy her a book she likes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.03,0:20:00.10,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I put some money and a card in this envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:02.29,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you give it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:06.08,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If I give it personally, she may not accept it, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:09.13,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.38,0:20:11.91,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa-san really loves Maka, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.43,0:20:15.12,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Then leave it to Blair!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:18.31,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:25.16,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.25,0:20:27.65,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I got carried away and bought something for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:32.17,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost to temptation...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.55,0:20:35.24,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Blair is easily tempted...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:38.22,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This cat-witch sure is bad, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:42.92,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If I change the size with magic It'll be perfect for Maka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.06,0:20:45.30,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Pum-Pumpkin, pumpkin...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:51.21,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Card inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:53.62,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:20:55.12,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:57.37,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I made pumpkin pie so let's eat some.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:20:58.67,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:01.95,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a present from Papa-san to Maka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.66,0:21:04.57,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a gift because of the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:07.97,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:10.50,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Tada!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.28,0:21:19.53,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving perverted underwear to his daughter, is he serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:21.03,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Maka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:23.93,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:25.08,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:28.88,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,"Congratulations!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.24,0:21:31.54,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,"Studying was pretty tough, right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:36.82,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,"I sent this present hoping that you'll have a good time with it."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:38.21,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,"From Papa with love."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.12,0:21:40.92,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,How would I have a "good time"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.33,0:21:45.90,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he intend to make me into some kind of perverted daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:55.58,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,She should be pretty happy by know, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.95,0:21:58.64,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,He's really the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.84,0:22:01.95,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.04,0:22:04.85,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Maka...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.81,0:22:10.81,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.24,0:23:42.63,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok, let's go over answers now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.66,0:23:43.77,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,, Nagata-kun from Media Factory,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.38,0:23:47.18,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,if you're going to do this much work on math problems, get them right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.76,0:23:49.05,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The next is boss of Bones, Minami-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.56,0:23:50.46,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Your writing's horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.57,0:23:52.57,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't write Nirvash, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.26,0:23:54.50,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And Higashiyama-kun from Dentsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.06,0:23:58.86,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't Dragon Quest, and I won't go easy on you just because you're the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.39,0:24:02.92,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok, and with that we finish up.
