Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.12,0:24:13.40,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't scribble or write rants on the tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.44,0:24:15.92,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially Omigawa-kun, why did you even fill up the back page?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.95,0:24:20.20,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And Yamatoya who sent us a letter,\N no one knows your birthday, so don't get cocky, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.67,0:24:22.49,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And now for the worst of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.20,0:24:25.67,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Higarashi-kun, keep your jokes to a minimum.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.67,0:24:27.00,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't try, we'll have another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.00,0:24:28.45,Soul Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,So make sure to keep up on the studies.
